Senior Sales Manager
#удаленка #senior #300k
Company: Vinteo.ai 
Salary:Base salary of $3000;
Vinteo specializes in automating the process of creating product images, offering a solution that allows for quick visualization of products in realistic interiors. 
The service creates images for product cards, making it an excellent tool for e-commerce stores and marketplace sellers, as everyone competes in the endless race to enhance their product appeal.
Our solution stands out in the market with its tangible benefits, primarily in time and cost savings, which are easily demonstrable to potential clients.
What we offer:
— Base salary of $3000;
— After passing a probationary period (duration to be discussed), excellent commission on each subscription to the service, as well as a percentage of every subsequent monthly payment for the first year. Successful KPI achievement can potentially double total income;
— Freedom to choose your sales approach and influence the product;
— Remote work format. 
Requirements:
— At least 3 years of experience in selling SaaS products – mandatory;
— Proven track record in client acquisition, attraction, and B2B negotiations;
— Experience in finding clients through Facebook, LinkedIn, and other resources;
— Experience with CRM systems;
— Fluent in English. Knowledge of Russian as a second language is welcome.
